:{"pid":"b7448918a5390d20c2d15a52c85cf7b1a6d91e61","tid":2431791,"uid":141863,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:59:35.000Z","msg":"瞳內童乃僮<br />\n<br />\nsorry 亂試"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"點解<br />\n中文 u sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"眼中所看見的那個小孩原來是位書僮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"再sad dd <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25decc1406823c069ff06097d284dc83996e37cf","tid":2431791,"uid":141863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e5f4257daedd0f9bd8484f4a373da8fe8042d1d","tid":2431791,"uid":393441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3dea4214f8ec82d275f90fa0637fe17f6eea4877","tid":2431791,"uid":315645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7448918a5390d20c2d15a52c85cf7b1a6d91e61","tid":2431791,"uid":141863,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:59:35.000Z","msg":"瞳內童乃僮<br />\n<br />\nsorry 亂試"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"點解<br />\n中文 u sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"眼中所看見的那個小孩原來是位書僮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"要配返寵同埋籠, 有囚禁感,所以僮係奴僕個隻, 唔只係書僮"},{"pid":"81c1891d75c7a12ee2353fe376744108e2ea07c6","tid":2431791,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"好多好句，不過應該對唔到<br />\n重點係三個字三個部首，一個common"},{"pid":"5d0bb2f1861b2430593bf959aeb7c86aee86d001","tid":2431791,"uid":393441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"籠中龍為寵<br />\n幞下菐為僕<br />\n<br />\n意解:<br />\n幞： &lt;名&gt; 形聲。字從巾從菐，菐亦聲。 &ldquo;菐&rdquo;意為&ldquo;外皮&rdquo;、&ldquo;外衣&rdquo;。 &ldquo;巾&rdquo;與&ldquo;菐&rdquo;聯合起來表示&ldquo;包裹用的布巾&rdquo;。<br />\n本義：頭巾。包東西的布<br />\n<br />\n菐者，瀆菐也。从丵从廾，廾亦聲。凡菐之屬皆从菐。蒲沃切〖注〗臣鉉等曰：「瀆，讀爲煩瀆之瀆。」一本注云：「丵，衆多也。兩手奉之，是煩瀆也。」<br />\n<br />\n僕者<br />\n(1)　受僱做雜事的人。如：「僕人」、「女僕」、「奴僕」、「老僕」。<br />\n(2)　「我」的謙稱。如：「僕自小好為文章，以至於今。」<br />\n<br />\n因此，如上句為囚困於籠中之龍，表哀愁之意<br />\n<br />\n是故下聯解為：幞下菐為僕<br />\n「以布巾包裹著頭部的那些眾多做著煩瀆工作之人，正是那些受僱做事／被放逐離家別井的奴僕。"},{"pid":"05ed2bf2c41dcd2b59c139d25adf45aa7d8062e9","tid":2431791,"uid":213913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"森中木為林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b634234533bec4ec36a87796f054e1e9390367","tid":2431791,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25decc1406823c069ff06097d284dc83996e37cf","tid":2431791,"uid":141863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e5f4257daedd0f9bd8484f4a373da8fe8042d1d","tid":2431791,"uid":393441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3dea4214f8ec82d275f90fa0637fe17f6eea4877","tid":2431791,"uid":315645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"點解<br />\n中文 u sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"眼中所看見的那個小孩原來是位書僮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"要配返寵同埋籠, 有囚禁感,所以僮係奴僕個隻, 唔只係書僮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c1d057cc96bfe21d052fe781e86d2b4873e8c7","tid":2431791,"uid":232575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:02:50.0